{"type": "article", "id": 44805, "title": "陈坤代言FILA，又有几个蹭“嘻哈”热点的广告 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2017-09-04T04:37:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 43780, "name": "中国有嘻哈"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170904113306OjrSMZmC91RtLowA.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 45.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"http://sports.sina.com.cn/outdoor/2017-09-01/doc-ifykpysa2519722.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>陈坤担任意大利品牌 FILA 代言人</b></a>，去年，品牌还曾签下高圆圆作为代言人。不过看这宣传海报，能给“厂花”换套衣服再拍吗？</p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 19.0px; font: 14.0px 'Helvetica Neue'} span.s1 {font: 13.0px 'Helvetica Neue'} </style>  </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170904114052LybrVNOq8R6jXUdx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.555385\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的广告</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/brand-marketing/american-express-built-a-game-that-lets-you-play-tennis-against-an-ai-opponent-at-the-u-s-open/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>运通在美国公开赛做了个 AI 游戏</b></a>，不需要穿戴任何外界的装备就可以打网球。代言人小威也到现场来为运通的粉丝体验中心站台，之前还拍了一支美网的预热广告。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170904114239M20H7Dh5SFxeGrlf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.547619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709041142491EUfoKC2p4dc9A6e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561798\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333; min-height: 21.0px} span.s1 {font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 14.0px Arial; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/42024\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>PGone 应邀为英雄联盟创作全新单曲《PentaKill》</b></a>，这位《中国有嘻哈》选手本身也是个游戏少年。网瘾少年们可以感受一下歌词里的游戏语言，脑海里大概可以直接打出一波骚操作了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=r0024dsdetd&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/42020\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>又一个嘻哈相关，小青龙为饿了么作词谱曲的单曲《饿》</b></a>，之前他也给魅族、快手写过广告歌。虽然很早被淘汰，但感觉成了一个活在广告里的“选手”，歌词似乎越来越没有营养了。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=w0544x0ro4o&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 45.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333; min-height: 22.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 45.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>除此之外，在最新一集《中国有嘻哈》，中插的农夫山泉口播广告再次升级，这次的广告形式换成了孙八一和 PG One、小白的 Battle。</p><p class=\"\">考虑到下周六就是节目最后一期，这波热点，品牌大概蹭的也差不多了。</p><p><b><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NjEzNDI4MA==&amp;mid=2652082229&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=36c355f11f45a7d3d6572e322360f7a6&amp;chksm=bd0adcd28a7d55c4f8730dc248e377a94df75c2409cc45491e05716e2ab0317da62cb2c61068&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0901r7nesRQDe4iZfLq4Kt9Y#rd\" rel=\"nofollow\">天猫酒水节给各种酒出了一套扑克</a></b>，没错，又一个天猫造出来的节，今年是第二届。大怪、小怪分别是绝对伏特加和猴王 47 黑森林干金酒。还挺好看的，想看完整版的可以<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NjEzNDI4MA==&amp;mid=2652082229&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=36c355f11f45a7d3d6572e322360f7a6&amp;chksm=bd0adcd28a7d55c4f8730dc248e377a94df75c2409cc45491e05716e2ab0317da62cb2c61068&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0901r7nesRQDe4iZfLq4Kt9Y#rd\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里</a>查看。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170904115926crO04PSbWNIlGnER.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.778125\" data-format=\"webp\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170904115936xByPH6m0hJs2WYe4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.778125\" data-format=\"webp\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'Songti SC'; color: #ed2325; -webkit-text-stroke: #ed2325} span.s1 {font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-kerning: none; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s2 {font: 18.0px Georgia; font-kerning: none; color: #ed2325} span.s3 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/brand-marketing/bedding-startup-brooklinen-used-crowd-sourced-images-from-pet-influencers-for-its-new-campaign/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>寝具品牌&nbsp;Brooklinen&nbsp;最新营销</b></a>，找的是一群网红宠物来拍广告，还蛮萌的。<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Brooklinen</span>&nbsp;是一家位于布鲁克林的初创公司，以低廉的价格出售豪华酒店品质的床单。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170904120358o7yeArmDH0xuLaOC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684270\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170904120351H0merCTv2lojAZKR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665169\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px Georgia; color: #ed2325; -webkit-text-stroke: #ed2325} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>还有些你可能感兴趣的数字</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.adquan.com/post-2-42026.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>6.5 万亿</b></a>——2017 年中国网络零售市场交易额预计达 6. 5 万亿。艾媒咨询发布《2017上半年中国品质电商专题研究报告》，2016 年中国网络零售市场交易额达 5.15 万亿元，移动购物市场交易额为 3.41 万亿元，移动购物市场交易额占比达 66.2%。</p><p class=\"\">26-35 岁是电商用户的主力大军，女性和男性的用户比例大约在 6：4，好像也没什么太多意外吧。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170904120833m4thEkPUMC3zfv1N.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.497143\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">题图来源：<a href=\"http://sports.sina.com.cn/outdoor/2017-09-01/doc-ifykpysa2519722.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\">sina</a></p>"}